&lt;p&gt;本篇環境使用版本:&lt;br&gt;&lt;a href=&quot;https://download.qt.io/official_releases/qt/5.10/5.10.1/&quot; target=&quot;_blank&quot; rel=&quot;noopener&quot;&gt;QT 5.10.1&lt;/a&gt;
      
    
    </summary>
    
